        <h3 class="expanded">Legal Disclaimer</h3>
        <p>At Jaguar Land Rover we are committed to protecting the privacy of the users of our Live Help customer service tool. The following information will give you the details about what happens when you visit our website, what information is obtained from you and how (if at all) we use this information.</p>
    
