            <div class="accordion__text">
             <p>What information do we collect from LAND ROVER Live Help users? During the engagement, LAND ROVER Live Help enters into a live question and answer session with an agent either by text chat or social media messenger service. We maintain dialogue transcripts of these chats. After the chat, we ask LAND ROVER Live Help customers to fill out an exit survey in order to obtain valuable feedback about the levels of our service. Moreover, all personal data is only collected if you voluntarily supply it, e.g. when completing a contact form. If during the engagement the user chooses to enter personal or business data (email addresses, names, addresses), the disclosure of such data is done so by the user on a voluntary basis. Such information is not passed to any third parties or used for any other purpose(s) than that/those requested by the customer. We log browser information (e.g. Internet Protocol addresses and browser types) to help diagnose problems with our service, gather broad demographic information and administer our site. By choosing to engage in a chat and use the services, the user consents to such logging and processing of IP address.</p><p></p>
            </div>
          </div>
           <div class="liveagent__block">
            <input type="checkbox" id="accordion17" name="accordion17" />
            <label class="accordion__title" for="accordion17">How does Jaguar Land Rover use information it collects from LAND ROVER Live Help users and will Jaguar Land Rover disclose such information to outside parties?</label>
            <div class="accordion__text">
             <p> We access the information we collect for certain purposes (for example, to aggregate the information, to monitor the use of the service during certain engagements and for other lawful purposes). All LAND ROVER Live Help user information, including sensitive personal information, will not be shared with anyone. We do not sell, trade or rent the personal information or sensitive personal information that LAND ROVER Live Help users provide. Jaguar Land Rover may store and use such information and data for JLR marketing purposes to assist customers in procuring Jaguar Land Rover products as well as to provide any details about Jaguar Land Rover products. 

For more information about how Jaguar Land Rover and its group companies handle and protect your Information, please refer to our JLR Group Privacy Policy at https://www.landrover.in/privacy-policy.html 
</p>
            </div>
          </div>         
          <div class="liveagent__block">
            <input type="checkbox" id="accordion13" name="accordion13" />
